fields.name: Evening Meditation
fields.description: A peaceful evening meditation led by Edel. For anyone who is looking to explore a more peaceful journey with their mind, this is for you.

fields.name: Inversion Training

fields.description: If you are interested in learning the art of breathwork, come along to this workshop. It can do wonders for relaxation.
